{"id":252705,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/09/维权网-河南访民张玉层控告公安机关是村霸的黑/","date":"2012-09-19T07:30:47Z","modified":"2012-09-19T07:30:47Z","title":"维权网 | 河南访民张玉层控告公安机关是村霸的黑保护伞（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员关小令报道）家住河南省平顶山市汝州市蟒川乡代湾村的女访民张玉层，因遭邻居郭金凤不断投毒、盗窃寻衅兹事，给其家庭造成巨大经济损失和人身伤害案件，汝州市公安局不仅不立案查处，反而对受害人采取多非法拘留关押手段进行所谓维稳迫害。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>访民张玉层控诉说，她家于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1999</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月在本村开办了一个商店，招至也是开店邻居郭金凤的疾恨与不满，认为抢了她家的生意，就仗着她儿子代春卫是村支部副书记的势力，遂对张玉层家不断产生报复行为，并在商店开张不几天，张玉层家的商店大门就被人趁夜砸坏，向公安机关报案不处理，从此更严重的报复事件频频发生。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2000</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>，张玉层家喂养的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>头约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>公斤重的小猪被人投毒，全部死掉。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2001</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>，张玉层家的一头即将产崽的母猪再次被投毒药死。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2001</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日</span><span>，张玉层家</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>头将要出拦的大肥猪又被投毒药死。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2004</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日</span><span>，村支部副书记代春卫公开将张玉层家</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">280</span><span>棵杨树砍伐卖掉。同年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月，代春卫又抢收张玉层家</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>分多亩地玉米。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2005</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>，张玉层家一头即将产仔的大母牛又被毒死。同月，代春卫又将张玉层家</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>分多地的成熟小麦抢收。同年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月，郭金凤用村委会高音喇叭对张玉层一家老小进行辱骂，当其他村干部扯断电线制止后，郭金凤又手持脸盆敲打骂遍全村。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日</span><span>夜晚，张玉层家</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2.8</span><span>亩地玉米全被人用刀砍倒。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2009</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>日</span><span>下午，代春卫儿子代芳芳等人将张玉层丈夫代新林推入大水坑中，幸被村民代大军及时发现救起。当晩，代春卫又雇佣手下成员将张玉层家准备建房用的两大车石头，全部扔进大水坑里。第二天，代春卫又砍伐张玉层家杨树</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">75</span><span>棵。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>数年来，张玉层与丈夫代新林多次遭到郭金凤一家人的毒打，件件事都向乡派出所和汝州市公安局报案无果，十多年的上访，反遭汝州市公安局非法多次拘留关押，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日</span><span>，汝州市公安局以张玉层“聚众扰乱社会秩序罪”</span><span> </span><span>拘留，期间汝州市公安局政委刘亚哲同乡派出所所长张志卫逼迫张玉层写“停访息诉书”，</span><span> </span><span>并保证说“只要你同意停访息诉，立即放人”。</span><span> </span><span>被张玉层拒绝后，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>对张玉层执行逮捕决定，但在将张玉层逮捕关押</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">65</span><span>天后，不审不判又放出监狱。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>日</span><span>，汝州市公安局解除对朱喜才监视居住，解除对张玉层、佑存、吴晓娜、夏会轻</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>访民的取保候审决定。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">21</span><span>日</span><span>，汝州市公安局又作出对朱喜才、张玉层、佑存、吴晓娜、夏会轻</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>位访民监视居住的决定。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日</span><span>，汝州市公安局再次以这</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>位访民“涉嫌聚众扰乱社会秩序”</span><span> </span><span>罪收监，同时报请汝州市检察院，汝州市检察院指派该院公诉科检察官王霞对五访民进行非法指控公诉。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">21</span><span>日</span><span>，汝州市公安局又作出对五访民监视居住的决定。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>，汝州市公安局又以张玉层“扰乱公共场所秩序罪”</span><span> </span><span>给予行政拘留十日的处罚。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>访民张玉层说，我们村支部副书记代春卫就是官府任命的村霸王，是公安机关利用黑社会欺负百姓的管理手段和工具，所以，对代春卫一家的刑事犯罪不追究，反而放纵，完全是官黑一家，不给百姓留下生活下去的希望，我上访十多年，各级政府不作为，我们百姓的生命财产没有法律的保障，贪官恶官不断提拔升官，形成层层包庇，是当今中国社会普遍黑暗的根源，我只能拼上老命告下去，警醒中央最高领导人的重视。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-uSwF7vfCUAc/UFlbDa-JpyI/AAAAAAAAO6U/vfYXiot_rRY/s1600/%E5%BC%A0%E7%8E%89%E5%B1%82.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-uSwF7vfCUAc/UFlbDa-JpyI/AAAAAAAAO6U/vfYXiot_rRY/s320/%E5%BC%A0%E7%8E%89%E5%B1%82.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-WCzAqsGMKnk/UFlbLYvpPhI/AAAAAAAAO6c/tQxfK0vhsHA/s1600/%E5%BC%A0%E7%8E%89%E5%B1%82%E6%8B%98%E7%95%99%E4%B9%A6.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-WCzAqsGMKnk/UFlbLYvpPhI/AAAAAAAAO6c/tQxfK0vhsHA/s320/%E5%BC%A0%E7%8E%89%E5%B1%82%E6%8B%98%E7%95%99%E4%B9%A6.JPG\" width=\"231\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-1195418726289583809?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}